Tanıtılan With innovative Presswing technology, the new NxtCut WING shapes scrap more efficiently – perfect for small to mid-sized yards facing changing material demands.
Choose between 800 or 1,000 tons of shear force, and two bed lengths – 6.2 m (compact) or 8 m (spacious) – to match your operation.
Smart details like a generous overstroke function ensure optimal material handling, better compaction, and reduced wear.
A forged blade slide with hardened supports prevents deformation – for long-lasting reliability.

The NxtCut WING brings next-level performance to your yard.

Tanıtılan The 400 bar hydraulic system of the NxtCut WING delivers unmatched performance.

This means faster cylinder movement, optimized acceleration and deceleration, and full control at every step.
Thanks to hydraulic separation of pump flows, the system allows simultaneous cylinder actions – boosting overall productivity.
With the world’s smallest tank volume, 5 μm oil filtration, pipework instead of hoses, and dynamic oil level monitoring, maintenance becomes minimal – and reliability, maximum.
Precision-engineered. Built for uptime. Designed by LINDEMANN. The 400 bar hydraulic system of the NxtCut WING delivers unmatched performance – with performance- and flow-controlled pumps that adjust to your needs in real time.
